<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>공지사항 목록</title>
  <link href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

<%- include('../menu.html') %>

<div class="container">
  <p></p>
  <div>
    <h1 class="mt-4">인터넷뱅킹 고객센터</h1>
    <% if (user && user.user_type === 'admin') { %>
        <p></p>
        <h5>관리자로 로그인 되었습니다.</h5>
        <p></p>
    <% } %>
  </div>
  <p></p>


  <!-- 탭 메뉴 -->
  <ul class="nav nav-tabs">
    <li class="nav-item">
      <a class="nav-link <%= category === 'default' ? 'active' : '' %>" href="/board/list/default">기본</a>
    </li>
    <li class="nav-item">
      <a class="nav-link <%= category === 'notice' ? 'active' : '' %>" href="/board/list/notice">공지사항</a>
    </li>
    <li class="nav-item">
      <a class="nav-link <%= category === 'event' ? 'active' : '' %>" href="/board/list/event">이벤트</a>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <div class="mb-3 mt-3">

    <% if (user && user.user_type === 'admin') { %>
      <a href="/board/insert" class="btn btn-primary"> 글 작성 </a>
    <% } %>
  </div>

  <table class="table table-striped">
    <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>No.</th>
      <th>제목</th>
      <th>작성일</th>
      <% if (user && user.user_type === 'admin') { %>
      <th>삭제</th>
      <% } %>
    </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
    <% let itemNo = (currentPage - 1) * 10 + 1; %>
    <% data.forEach(board => { %>
      <tr>
        <td><%= itemNo++ %></td>
        <td><a href="/board/content/<%= board.board_id %>"><%= board.title %></a></td>
        <td><%= board.created_at %></td>
        <% if (user && user.user_type === 'admin') { %>
        <td>
          <form action="/board/delete" method="post" onsubmit="return confirm('정말 삭제하시겠습니까?');">
            <input type="hidden" name="board_id" value="<%= board.board_id %>">
            <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="<%= csrfToken %>">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger btn-sm">삭제</button>
          </form>
        </td>
        <% } %>
      </tr>
    <% }) %>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <!-- Pagination -->
  <nav aria-label="Page navigation">
    <ul class="pagination">
      <% if (currentPage > 1) { %>
        <li class="page-item">
          <a class="page-link" href="/board/list/<%= category %>?page=<%= currentPage - 1 %>" aria-label="Previous">
            <span aria-hidden="true">&laquo;</span>
          </a>
        </li>
      <% } %>
      <% for (let i = 1; i <= totalPages; i++) { %>
        <li class="page-item <%= i === currentPage ? 'active' : '' %>">
          <a class="page-link" href="/board/list/<%= category %>?page=<%= i %>"><%= i %></a>
        </li>
      <% } %>
      <% if (currentPage < totalPages) { %>
        <li class="page-item">
          <a class="page-link" href="/board/list/<%= category %>?page=<%= currentPage + 1 %>" aria-label="Next">
            <span aria-hidden="true">&raquo;</span>
          </a>
        </li>
      <% } %>
    </ul>
  </nav>
</div>


<div class="footer">
  © 2024 클라우드 엔지니어 양성 과정 1기생 Mini Project 4팀. 모든 권리 보유.
</div>

<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
